item.title: Prayer bpn4137 in Canadian Indigenous
item.description: O Miyaani Da’a’ntgi Lusndaamti sü gugweelksm laawksi ada so goy’p’m biyaalsi.and Nüün gu daanmsgit di£ na gatgyedn. *O God, Guide me protect me make of me a shining lamp and a brilliant star. Thou art the Mighty And the Powerful. (Source category: Sm’algyax) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 4137)
